"""
        Test that a TypeError is raised when an invalid value is used to set
        the private key unique identifier of a CreateKeyPair response payload.
        """
kwargs = {'private_key_unique_identifier': 0}
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Private key unique identifier must be a string.', payloads.
    CreateKeyPairResponsePayload, **kwargs)
args = payloads.CreateKeyPairResponsePayload(
    ), 'private_key_unique_identifier', 0
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Private key unique identifier must be a string.', setattr, *args)
